of BMC</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike\">Best road bikes 2025 reviewed and rated</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h2>BMC Teammachine SLR specs, weights and prices</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"544\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-970x544.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-970x544.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-300x168.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-768x431.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-1536x861.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-2048x1148.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-750x420.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/02/BMC-2026-Teammachine-SLR-THREE-red-blk-blk-glam-key-4-1140x639.jpg 1140w\" /><figcaption>BMC </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Teammachine SLR is available from today in three specs, with a highest One spec due later this year. The US dollar and Euro price is the same, with UK pricing yet to be announced.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The good news is that the Gen 4.5 bikes are cheaper than their predecessors. Whereas the Teammachine SLR Two was previously priced at €5,699, the new bike costs €4,999. The price for the Three spec decreases from €5,499 to €3,999 and the Four spec drops from €4,799 to €2,999.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>BMC Teammachine SLR Two</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Groupset: </strong>Shimano Ultegra Di2 (R8150) 52/36 x 11-34t</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels: </strong>BMC AR 27 Tubeless Ready, 27mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tyres:</strong> Pirelli P Zero Road, 26mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight:</strong> 8kg claimed</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price:</strong> $/€4,999</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>BMC Teammachine SLR Three</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Groupset: </strong>Shimano 105 Di2 (R7150) 50/34 x 11-34t</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels: </strong>Shimano TC 500 hubs and PRD23, 23mm rim</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tyres:</strong> Pirelli P Zero Road Sport, 26mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight:</strong> 8.3kg claimed</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price:</strong> $/€3,999</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>BMC Teammachine SLR Four</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Groupset: </strong>Shimano 105 (R7100) 50/34 x 11-34t</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheels: </strong>Shimano TC 500 hubs and PRD23, 23mm rim</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tyres:</strong> Pirelli P7 Sport, 26mm</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Weight:</strong> 8.5kg claimed </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price:</strong> $/€2,999</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/newsletters\"><img width=\"970\" height=\"351\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-970x351.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-970x351.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-300x109.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-768x278.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-1536x556.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-2048x741.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-750x271.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/10/Newsletter-flash-1-1140x412.jpg 1140w\" /></a><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n<p>